<p>Burn This (stylized as Burn/This for the 2019 revival) is a play by <ref target="/wiki/Lanford_Wilson" title="Lanford Wilson">Lanford Wilson</ref>. Like much of Wilson's work, the play includes themes of <ref target="/wiki/Gay" title="Gay">gay</ref> identity and relationships.</p>

